bradtaniguchi-dev

This repo represents my portfolio/blog site that is hosted on github-pages.

This repo will be updated to replace the current one at: https://github.com/bradtaniguchi/bradtaniguchi.github.io

Which uses a custom domain at: https://bradtaniguchi.dev/

issue.title: [Feature] Update activity feed
issue.body:
**Describe the solution you'd like**
The activity feed should integrate the following:
- github, via: https://docs.github.com/en/rest/activity/events#list-public-events-for-a-user
- codewars via: https://www.npmjs.com/package/codewars-node-api
- freeCodeCamp via: ???
- blog posts via: self-loading+dev.to integration
- snippets via: https://docs.github.com/en/rest/gists/gists

